{"tid":6628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魚販撞壞林寶堅尼　車主竟婉拒賠償","createTime":"2016-11-27T12:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T07:21:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f7ba459610c3f54511bf66d8b75756c90657337","tid":6628,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161127/420_c9d75e0a72808bb8d457f814f1cf784f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161127%2F420_c9d75e0a72808bb8d457f814f1cf784f.jpg&h=2246f2f1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n泰國中部暖武里府周四發生一宗交通意外，一對賣魚夫婦駕駛一部老舊轎車，不慎撞到停在前方的林寶堅尼跑車。跑車車主沒追究魚販責任，還請他們把修車費用轉捐給寺廟行善，代替賠償。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161127/420_c3a466133beaf7f11694b2d18c615765.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161127%2F420_c3a466133beaf7f11694b2d18c615765.jpg&h=98deccba&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事發當天，魚販的車輛停在一部林寶堅尼後方時，不慎誤採油門，汽車暴衝撞到前方的林寶堅尼，名車的車身被刮花。魚販夫婦表示願意賠償，並提出每月賠償3000泰銖（約2600元台幣），以分期償還修車費。 <br />\n<br />\n車主卻說，魚販可以分期付款10個月償還3萬泰銖（約2.6萬元台幣），但不是賠償給他，而是將錢捐到寺廟行善，以代替賠償。 <br />\n<br />\n車主謙虛回應：「我這樣做不是炫耀自己富有，只是想讓大家學會原諒、微笑。雖然車子很貴，但又怎麼樣？如果不是故意撞到，我們應該敞開胸懷原諒他人。」他又指，大家都是泰國人，應該互相鼓勵幫助。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161127/420_ab2367798b4bfd236bd592e8afc9cf2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161127%2F420_ab2367798b4bfd236bd592e8afc9cf2f.jpg&h=eb60e481&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有網友反應，泰國人天性不計較。香港網友Sun Poon分享經驗，在泰國玩時，曾不小心撞到別人的車。車主不但不願意收賠償，還問泰國好玩嗎？要他以後開車小心，「泰國人真是好的不得了」。 <br />\n<br />\n網友Dicky Wong則表示，車主真大方，無論是裝的或是真心的，「都已經開林寶堅尼了，不會為了一萬八千跟窮人計較，還叫人捐去做慈善，實在很讚」。 <br />\n<br />\n（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"9d4b18a141db83adca133d7a7b8b2cfbbf6f889f","tid":6628,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"香港會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8d3140031f7f7a07380a691dbcc3c3a2079afa","tid":6628,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n告到個呀伯仆街"},{"pid":"4996ef8c12a711f0b4d24be646f94d3bc2a18f1e","tid":6628,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n告到個<span style=\"color: red;\">魚販</span>仆街</blockquote>"},{"pid":"39fa08ff1852aafee5917e2509da37c98ebe5d47","tid":6628,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"咁有善心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75ec196991c945c31e6c0d5a4bd45e88848838a","tid":6628,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:28:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66ddb299f87128324f218e38edd9462131ba6494","tid":6628,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"如果係大陸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n給我往死裹打"},{"pid":"b1ca41d0eb85e3c2f039dfc77acc7c74dfca2216","tid":6628,"uid